languages.text: Не понимая, чем заслужили такую благосклонность от мон-кай, эльдары скупо благодарят Вольного Торговца. Как только бригада техников завершает ремонтные работы, ксеносы поспешно покидают систему.

traits.locale_text: Не понимая, чем заслужили такую благосклонность от мон-кай, эльдары скупо благодарят Вольного Торговца. Как только бригада техников завершает ремонтные работы, ксеносы поспешно покидают систему.

languages.text: The Aeldari half-heartedly thank the Rogue Trader, not understanding what earned them the favour of the mon-keigh. As soon as the technicians finish the repairs, the xenos hastily leave the system.

languages.text: 那些艾达灵族敷衍地感谢着行商浪人，不明白是什么原因让他们赢得了猴子的青睐。技术人员刚刚完成维修，那些异形就匆忙离开了星系。
languages.original_text: The Aeldari half-heartedly thank the Rogue Trader, not understanding what earned them the favour of the mon-keigh. As soon as the technicians finish the repairs, the xenos hastily leave the system.

traits.locale_text: 那些艾达灵族敷衍地感谢着行商浪人，不明白是什么原因让他们赢得了猴子的青睐。技术人员刚刚完成维修，那些异形就匆忙离开了星系。

languages.text: アエルダリは、なぜモン＝ケイが自分たちに好意を抱いたのかを理解しないまま、中途半端に自由開拓者に感謝した。技術者たちが修理を終えると、異種族たちは急いで星系を去った。
languages.original_text: The Aeldari half-heartedly thank the Rogue Trader, not understanding what earned them the favour of the mon-keigh. As soon as the technicians finish the repairs, the xenos hastily leave the system.

traits.locale_text: アエルダリは、なぜモン＝ケイが自分たちに好意を抱いたのかを理解しないまま、中途半端に自由開拓者に感謝した。技術者たちが修理を終えると、異種族たちは急いで星系を去った。

languages.text: Los Aeldari dan las gracias a regañadientes a{mf|l| la} Comerciante Independiente, sin entender por qué se han ganado el favor de los mon-keigh. En cuanto los técnicos terminan las reparaciones, los xenos se disponen a abandonar el sistema.
languages.original_text: The Aeldari half-heartedly thank the Rogue Trader, not understanding what earned them the favour of the mon-keigh. As soon as the technicians finish the repairs, the xenos hastily leave the system.

traits.locale_text: Los Aeldari dan las gracias a regañadientes a{mf|l| la} Comerciante Independiente, sin entender por qué se han ganado el favor de los mon-keigh. En cuanto los técnicos terminan las reparaciones, los xenos se disponen a abandonar el sistema.

languages.text: Die Aeldari danken {mf|dem Freihändler|der Freihändlerin} halbherzig. Sie begreifen nicht, was ihnen die Gunst des Chem-Pan-Sey eingebracht hat. Sobald die Techniker die Reparaturen abgeschlossen haben, verlassen die Xenos eilig das System.
languages.original_text: The Aeldari half-heartedly thank the Rogue Trader, not understanding what earned them the favour of the mon-keigh. As soon as the technicians finish the repairs, the xenos hastily leave the system.

traits.locale_text: Die Aeldari danken {mf|dem Freihändler|der Freihändlerin} halbherzig. Sie begreifen nicht, was ihnen die Gunst des Chem-Pan-Sey eingebracht hat. Sobald die Techniker die Reparaturen abgeschlossen haben, verlassen die Xenos eilig das System.

languages.text: Les Aeldaris remercient {mf|le libre-marchand|la libre-marchande} à demi-mot, sans comprendre ce qui leur a valu la bienveillance des mon-keigh. À peine les techniciens ont-ils terminé les réparations que les xénos quittent le système en toute hâte.
languages.original_text: The Aeldari half-heartedly thank the Rogue Trader, not understanding what earned them the favour of the mon-keigh. As soon as the technicians finish the repairs, the xenos hastily leave the system.

languages.text: Mon-keighlerin neden böyle bir iyilikte bulunduğunu anlamayan Aeldariler, Hür Tacir'e gönülsüzce teşekkür ediyor. Teknisyenler tamiri bitirir bitirmez zenolar, aceleyle sistemden ayrılıyor.
